      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-08-18T21:12:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a bit too general for my taste --- since the purpose of this CL was for verified boot, perhaps this CL should just keep that scope, and just point to some data structure with pre-parsed verified boot options.",
